Personally Im adult enuf to see behavior on both sides of an issue that I dont agree with.  I dont feel compelled to say I agree with 100% of a guildees actions , simply becuase Im guilded with him.<br>
<br>
I think both sides need to grow up a bit and make the decision to work together even if it means sacrificing something a time or two.<br>
<br>
Sssorn since you seem to think your all knowing..I expect this to fall on deaf ears , but you never know....If you really want to make a difference or make progress , try posting without the petty insults laced into your post and the air of superiority.  Im sure you would get better results , unless your intent is to actually bait people into flaming and avoiding the issue by responding out of anger to you.  You seem to be a BB veteran and prolly know this but figured I'd take a shot anyway.<br>
<br>
